      "review_summary": "The branch replaces selected provider plugin `response.json()` success reads with direct `readResponseWithLimit` plus `JSON.parse` calls and also reformats unrelated extension files.\n\nPR surface: Source +120, Tests -51. Total +69 across 60 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR defects: PR-head source shows parse-breaking constants and `Pick<Response, \"json\">` helpers passed to a full-`Response` reader. The original unbounded-read class is source-visible on current main, but this branch has no after-fix runtime proof.",
